fortify  [level 6]: one casts this targetting another healer
                    the targetted healer's next heal is at max rate 
                    (i.e. no random amount) at an ability level
                    of your level + healer's level at a cost of a 
                    heal normally cast  (note: more than one
                    healer may cast this on a healer)
                    
                    syntax: fortify <target>
                    
                    cost:  sp:10  xp:100  coins:500
                    